---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
---

<Layout title="Tools" description="Free, open-source tools to hold power accountable and protect your rights.">
  <section class="hero-mini">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 data-en="Tools for the People" data-es="Herramientas para el Pueblo">Tools for the People</h1>
      <p data-en="Free, open-source tools to hold power accountable and protect your rights. Built by the community, for the community." data-es="Herramientas gratuitas y de código abierto para exigir rendición de cuentas y proteger tus derechos. Hechas por la comunidad, para la comunidad.">
        Free, open-source tools to hold power accountable and protect your rights.
        Built by the community, for the community.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid grid--2">
        <a href="/tools/eviction-tracker" class="card tool-card">
          <div class="tool-card__badge" data-en="Data + Resources" data-es="Datos + Recursos">Data + Resources</div>
          <div class="tool-card__icon"><Icon name="lucide:bar-chart-3" size={28} /></div>
          <h2 data-en="Denver Eviction Tracker" data-es="Rastreador de Desalojos de Denver">Denver Eviction Tracker</h2>
          <p data-en="Eviction data from the Princeton Eviction Lab and Colorado Judicial Branch, plus defense resources for tenants facing eviction. Track the crisis and know your rights." data-es="Datos de desalojos del Laboratorio de Desalojos de Princeton y la Rama Judicial de Colorado, además de recursos de defensa para inquilinos que enfrentan desalojo. Rastrea la crisis y conoce tus derechos.">
            Eviction data from the Princeton Eviction Lab and Colorado Judicial Branch, plus defense resources for tenants facing eviction.
            Track the crisis and know your rights.
          </p>
          <span class="tool-card__link" data-en="Launch Tool →" data-es="Abrir Herramienta →">Launch Tool →</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/tools/eviction-data" class="card tool-card">
          <div class="tool-card__badge" data-en="Data Story" data-es="Historia de Datos">Data Story</div>
          <div class="tool-card__icon"><Icon name="lucide:trending-up" size={28} /></div>
          <h2 data-en="Eviction Crisis: By the Numbers" data-es="Crisis de Desalojos: En Números">Eviction Crisis: By the Numbers</h2>
          <p data-en="15,953 families faced eviction in 2025 — 72% above pre-pandemic levels. Scroll through the data: the surge, the neighborhoods hit hardest, and the safety net that's collapsing." data-es="15,953 familias enfrentaron desalojo en 2025 — 72% sobre niveles pre-pandemia. Desplázate por los datos: la oleada, los vecindarios más afectados, y la red de seguridad que colapsa.">
            15,953 families faced eviction in 2025 — 72% above pre-pandemic levels. Scroll through the data: the surge, the neighborhoods hit hardest, and the safety net that's collapsing.
          </p>
          <span class="tool-card__link" data-en="Explore Data →" data-es="Explorar Datos →">Explore Data →</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/tools/rent-calculator" class="card tool-card">
          <div class="tool-card__badge" data-en="Interactive" data-es="Interactivo">Interactive</div>
          <div class="tool-card__icon"><Icon name="lucide:calculator" size={28} /></div>
          <h2 data-en="Rent Control Calculator" data-es="Calculadora de Control de Alquiler">Rent Control Calculator</h2>
          <p data-en="Enter your current rent and see how much you'd save under Denver For All's rent stabilization plan. Compare with and without vacancy decontrol. Generate a shareable graphic for social media." data-es="Ingresa tu alquiler actual y mira cuánto ahorrarías con el plan de estabilización de alquileres de Denver Para Todos. Compara con y sin descontrol de vacantes. Genera un gráfico compartible para redes sociales.">
            Enter your current rent and see how much you'd save under Denver For All's rent stabilization plan.
            Compare with and without vacancy decontrol. Generate a shareable graphic for social media.
          </p>
          <span class="tool-card__link" data-en="Launch Tool →" data-es="Abrir Herramienta →">Launch Tool →</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/tools/campaign-finance" class="card tool-card">
          <div class="tool-card__badge" data-en="Follow the Money" data-es="Sigue el Dinero">Follow the Money</div>
          <div class="tool-card__icon"><Icon name="lucide:coins" size={28} /></div>
          <h2 data-en="Follow the Money" data-es="Sigue el Dinero">Follow the Money</h2>
          <p data-en="Council voting scorecard on progressive priorities, plus direct links to search campaign contributions on SearchLight Denver and Colorado TRACER. See how your council member votes -- and who funds them." data-es="Tarjeta de puntuación de votos del concejo en prioridades progresistas, más enlaces directos para buscar contribuciones de campaña en SearchLight Denver y Colorado TRACER. Mira cómo vota tu concejal -- y quién los financia.">
            Council voting scorecard on progressive priorities, plus direct links to search campaign contributions on SearchLight Denver and Colorado TRACER.
            See how your council member votes -- and who funds them.
          </p>
          <span class="tool-card__link" data-en="Launch Tool →" data-es="Abrir Herramienta →">Launch Tool →</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/tools/know-your-rights" class="card tool-card">
          <div class="tool-card__badge" data-en="AI-Powered" data-es="Impulsado por IA">AI-Powered</div>
          <div class="tool-card__icon"><Icon name="lucide:gavel" size={28} /></div>
          <h2 data-en="Know Your Rights" data-es="Conoce Tus Derechos">Know Your Rights</h2>
          <p data-en="AI-powered tenant rights assistant available 24/7 in English and Spanish. Ask questions about eviction, repairs, deposits, discrimination, and more. Chat or call - powered by real legal knowledge, not generic AI." data-es="Asistente de derechos del inquilino impulsado por IA disponible 24/7 en inglés y español. Haz preguntas sobre desalojos, reparaciones, depósitos, discriminación y más. Chat o llamada - impulsado por conocimiento legal real, no IA genérica.">
            AI-powered tenant rights assistant available 24/7 in English and Spanish.
            Ask questions about eviction, repairs, deposits, discrimination, and more.
            Chat or call - powered by real legal knowledge, not generic AI.
          </p>
          <span class="tool-card__link" data-en="Launch Tool →" data-es="Abrir Herramienta →">Launch Tool →</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/tools/candidate-tracker" class="card tool-card">
          <div class="tool-card__badge" data-en="2027 Election" data-es="Elección 2027">2027 Election</div>
          <div class="tool-card__icon"><Icon name="lucide:users" size={28} /></div>
          <h2 data-en="Council Candidate Tracker" data-es="Rastreador de Candidatos del Concejo">Council Candidate Tracker</h2>
          <p data-en="Where do your City Council candidates stand on public safety, housing, and the issues that matter? Same ten questions sent to every candidate. Their answers — and silences — published unedited." data-es="¿Dónde se posicionan tus candidatos al Concejo Municipal sobre seguridad pública, vivienda y los temas que importan? Las mismas diez preguntas enviadas a cada candidato. Sus respuestas — y silencios — publicadas sin editar.">
            Where do your City Council candidates stand on public safety, housing, and the issues that matter?
            Same ten questions sent to every candidate. Their answers — and silences — published unedited.
          </p>
          <span class="tool-card__link" data-en="View Responses →" data-es="Ver Respuestas →">View Responses →</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/tools/mayoral-tracker" class="card tool-card">
          <div class="tool-card__badge" data-en="2027 Election" data-es="Elección 2027">2027 Election</div>
          <div class="tool-card__icon"><Icon name="lucide:landmark" size={28} /></div>
          <h2 data-en="Mayoral Tracker" data-es="Rastreador de Alcalde">Mayoral Tracker</h2>
          <p data-en="The mayor proposes the budget, runs the police, and vetoes legislation. Ten questions about executive power sent to every declared mayoral candidate. Johnston, Calderón, and challengers — on the record." data-es="El alcalde propone el presupuesto, dirige la policía y veta legislación. Diez preguntas sobre el poder ejecutivo enviadas a cada candidato declarado a alcalde. Johnston, Calderón y retadores — en el registro.">
            The mayor proposes the budget, runs the police, and vetoes legislation.
            Ten questions about executive power sent to every declared mayoral candidate.
          </p>
          <span class="tool-card__link" data-en="View Responses →" data-es="Ver Respuestas →">View Responses →</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/tools/money-in-politics" class="card tool-card">
          <div class="tool-card__badge" data-en="Data Story" data-es="Historia de Datos">Data Story</div>
          <div class="tool-card__icon"><Icon name="lucide:banknote" size={28} /></div>
          <h2 data-en="Money in Denver Politics" data-es="Dinero en la Política de Denver">Money in Denver Politics</h2>
          <p data-en="Outside spending exploded 380% from 2019 to 2023. Billionaire donors, real estate PACs, and the Fair Elections Fund. Scroll through who pays for Denver politics — and what they get." data-es="El gasto externo explotó 380% de 2019 a 2023. Donantes multimillonarios, PACs inmobiliarios, y el Fondo de Elecciones Justas. Desplázate para ver quién paga la política de Denver — y qué obtienen.">
            Outside spending exploded 380% from 2019 to 2023. Billionaire donors, real estate PACs, and the Fair Elections Fund. Scroll through who pays for Denver politics — and what they get.
          </p>
          <span class="tool-card__link" data-en="Explore Data →" data-es="Explorar Datos →">Explore Data →</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/tools/sidewalk-data" class="card tool-card">
          <div class="tool-card__badge" data-en="Data Story" data-es="Historia de Datos">Data Story</div>
          <div class="tool-card__icon"><Icon name="lucide:footprints" size={28} /></div>
          <h2 data-en="Sidewalk Data Explorer" data-es="Explorador de Datos de Aceras">Sidewalk Data Explorer</h2>
          <p data-en="43% of Denver's sidewalks are missing or deficient. Scroll through the data to see where the gaps are, which streets are most dangerous, and how transit access fails the neighborhoods that need it most." data-es="El 43% de las aceras de Denver faltan o son deficientes. Desplázate por los datos para ver dónde están las brechas, qué calles son más peligrosas, y cómo el acceso al transporte falla en los vecindarios que más lo necesitan.">
            43% of Denver's sidewalks are missing or deficient. Scroll through the data to see where the gaps are, which streets are most dangerous, and how transit access fails the neighborhoods that need it most.
          </p>
          <span class="tool-card__link" data-en="Explore Data →" data-es="Explorar Datos →">Explore Data →</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/tools/sponsor-tracker" class="card tool-card">
          <div class="tool-card__badge" data-en="2026 Session" data-es="Sesión 2026">2026 Session</div>
          <div class="tool-card__icon"><Icon name="lucide:scroll-text" size={28} /></div>
          <h2 data-en="State Sponsor Tracker" data-es="Rastreador de Patrocinadores Estatales">State Sponsor Tracker</h2>
          <p data-en="Track Colorado General Assembly legislators sponsoring bills aligned with our platform. See which state reps and senators are pushing progressive housing, labor, climate, and civil rights bills in the 2026 session." data-es="Rastrea a los legisladores de la Asamblea General de Colorado que patrocinan proyectos alineados con nuestra plataforma. Ve qué representantes y senadores impulsan proyectos progresistas de vivienda, trabajo, clima y derechos civiles en la sesión 2026.">
            Track Colorado General Assembly legislators sponsoring bills aligned with our platform.
            See which state reps and senators are pushing progressive housing, labor, climate, and civil rights bills in the 2026 session.
          </p>
          <span class="tool-card__link" data-en="View Sponsors →" data-es="Ver Patrocinadores →">View Sponsors →</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/tools/resistbot" class="card tool-card">
          <div class="tool-card__badge" data-en="Rapid Organizing" data-es="Organización Rápida">Rapid Organizing</div>
          <div class="tool-card__icon"><Icon name="lucide:send" size={28} /></div>
          <h2 data-en="Resistbot Campaigns" data-es="Campañas de Resistbot">Resistbot Campaigns</h2>
          <p data-en="Pre-written letter templates targeting every level of government. Copy a letter, text RESIST to 50409, and send it to your officials in under 2 minutes. Convert letters to petitions that anyone can sign." data-es="Plantillas de cartas pre-escritas dirigidas a todos los niveles de gobierno. Copia una carta, envía RESIST al 50409 y envíala a tus funcionarios en menos de 2 minutos. Convierte cartas en peticiones que cualquiera puede firmar.">
            Pre-written letter templates targeting every level of government.
            Copy a letter, text RESIST to 50409, and send it to your officials in under 2 minutes.
            Convert letters to petitions that anyone can sign.
          </p>
          <span class="tool-card__link" data-en="Launch Tool →" data-es="Abrir Herramienta →">Launch Tool →</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .hero-mini {
    padding: 4rem 0 3rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary) 0%, var(--color-secondary) 100%);
    color: white;
  }
  .hero-mini h1 { color: white; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .hero-mini p { font-size: 1.15rem; opacity: 0.9; max-width: 700px; }

  .tool-card {
    display: block;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    position: relative;
  }

  .tool-card__badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: 1.5rem;
    right: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--color-primary-light);
    color: var(--color-primary-dark);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }

  .tool-card__icon {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    border-radius: 14px;
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .tool-card h2 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .tool-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .tool-card__link {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }
</style>
